description: The Duke of Cambridge says relationships between people are "more essential" than legal treaties.
title: Prince William calls for 'strong bond' with Ireland after Brexit
title_page: Prince William calls for 'strong bond' with Ireland after Brexit - BBC News
maintext: "Of course, the changing relationship between the UK and the EU will require us to work together, to ensure that the relationship between Ireland and the UK remains just as strong," he said.
